metadata.name: The owl stands guard
metadata.description:
Screenz #1, By Fantomized. 

The Owl is a powerful protector symbol. This one carefully watches over your precious collection. The owl is also a dangerous predator. You don't want to have him on your way.  
Tresspassor be warned! 

Obviously, this is an allegory for a secure hardware wallet that shields your precious NFT collection from hackers!
